exceptions.exn: In environment x, y : R H1 : in_ucirc (fst (x, y)) (snd (x, y)) H2 : is_ratp (x, y) H3 : is_posp (x, y) Unable to unify "in_ucirc (fst (x, y)) (snd (x, y))" with "exists p q : Z, x = fst (ucp p q) /\\ y = snd (ucp p q) /\\ cond_pqb p q".

original: intros x y H. unfold in_ucp_setb. destruct H as [H1 [H2 H3]]. apply H1.
